Body: Date: Tue, 05 Nov 1996 00:20:41 GMT Server: NCSA/1.5 Content-type: text/html Last-modified: Thu, 10 Oct 1996 21:50:10 GMT Content-length: 797 Golfing at Torrey Pines I was in San Diego in June attending a conference, and I took the opportunity to hop over for some Golf at Torrey Pines Municipal GC, the home of the Buick Invitational.
